Royal seed pod is rewarded to the player by King Narnode Shareen after completing Monkey Madness II. Like the grand seed pod, this item can be used to teleport the player to the Grand Tree. Unlike the grand seed pod, the royal seed pod is not consumed upon use and never runs out of charges.

A player communes with the seed pod.

The royal seed pod will allow players to teleport at up to level 30 Wilderness. It, along with a Slayer ring, dragonstone teleportation jewellery and Pharaoh's sceptre, are the only available items to do so.

Additional pods may be purchased from King Narnode Shareen for 2 coins each.

'''Royal seed pod''' is rewarded to the player by [[King Narnode Shareen]] after completing [[Monkey Madness II]]. Like the [[grand seed pod]], this item can be used to teleport the player to the [[Grand Tree]]. Unlike the grand seed pod, the royal seed pod is not consumed upon use and never runs out of charges.
[[File:Squash Grand seed pod.gif|left|thumb|150px|A player communes with the seed pod.]]
The royal seed pod will allow players to teleport at up to level 30 [[Wilderness]]. It, along with a [[Slayer ring]], [[dragonstone]] [[teleportation jewellery]] and [[Pharaoh's sceptre]], are the only available items to do so.

Additional pods may be purchased from [[King Narnode Shareen]] for 2 coins each.
